($$4d1a1228-5e5f-4552-beaf-072c8fe4156e$$,$$U 243$$,$$B 68|L 452$$,59.5607,18.082,$$[holmlauk · uk · holmfrþ · lata · reisa · steina · eftʀ · fasta · uk · shfast · sunu · sina · þiʀ · to i hoitauaþum]$$,$$"Holmlaugʀ ok "Holmfriðr lata ræisa stæina æftiʀ "Fasta ok "Sigfast, sunu sina. Þæiʀ dou i hvitavaðum.$$,NULL,$$Holmlaugr and Holmfríðr have raised the stones in memory of Fasti and Sigfastr, their sons. They died in (their) christening robes.$$,NULL,NULL,$$Runsten$$,$$Sten$$,$$Uppland$$,$$Sweden$$),
